data.description: This is a modern, country style home in the up and coming city of Lake Wales. With neighboring towns such as Winter Haven, Dundee, and Haines City also being in short distance of travel this offers endless options for activities, shopping, and food. This home has new updates including fresh exterior and interior paint, new flooring in all three bedrooms, renovated front deck, and new landscaping. The living space is all open concept which allows the kitchen, dining, and living room to flow making the space feel airy and bright. With the bedrooms being split floor plan this allows for a large master bedroom and bath on its own  private side of the house. The additional bedrooms are nice sized with gracious closet space. The bedrooms also share space with a guest bathroom with a shower tub combo, and a laundry closet with additional storage. This home is not lacking in storage space with each bathroom equipped with linen closets, large walk in closet in the master bedroom, plenty of cabinet space in the kitchen and the island, a large garage, and even a shed in the yard! This home is also inclusive with a wheelchair accessible ramp installed in the two car garage. You can enjoy a nice cup of coffee on the all screened in lanai or on the large front porch! Don't miss your opportunity to enjoy this home with no HOA restrictions. Roof was replaced in 2018.
